  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To characterize the functional outcomes and prognostic factors for convulsive status
      epilepticus (SE) and to further develop and validate a simple and practicable scoring system
      for outcome prediction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      1. Retrospectively study all patients with convulsive SE treated between March, 2008, and
           November, 2014.

        2. Develop a scoring system for outcome prediction.

        3. Prospectively validate the predictive accuracy of the scoring system
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
